import { FontAwesomeIcon } from '@fortawesome/react-fontawesome';
import { faPaw, faHome, faCalendar, faRightFromBracket, faCircleCheck, faChevronDown } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons';

export const pets = <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faPaw} style={{color: "#000000", borderRadius:"50px", width:"35px", height:"35px", padding:"10px 10px 10px 10px", backgroundColor:"#6abcb4", border:"1px solid black", boxShadow: "5px 5px 0px 0px black" }} className="navbar-icon"/>
export const bookingIcon = <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faCalendar} style={{color: "#000000",}} className="navbar-icon"/>
export const home = <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faHome} style={{color: "#000000",}} className="navbar-icon"/>
export const signOutIcon = <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faRightFromBracket} style={{color: "#000000",}} className="navbar-icon"/>
export const checkIcon = <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faCircleCheck} style={{color: "#000000", width: "30px", height:"30px"}} />
export const downArrow = <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faChevronDown} style={{width:"40px", height:"40px"}}/>
